Package: datacamp
Type: Package
Title: Easily create interactive courses for www.DataCamp.com with R Markdown
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2013-09-07
Author: DataCamp
Maintainer: Filip Schouwenaars <filip@datacamp.com>
Description: This package makes it easy and fun to create interactive courses
    for www.DataCamp.com. All interactive exercises and course chapters are
    created and structured via R Markdown documents. The package has build-in
    functionality to effortlessly write Submission Correctness Tests for
    interactivity.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: www.datacamp.com
Imports:
    httr,
    RJSONIO,
    yaml,
    XML,
    RCurl,
    slidify
Suggests: 
    testthat
